front.title: •••Death Star Gunner
front.gametext: If on Death Star: Cumulatively adds 2 to total of Commence Primary Ignition. OR During your control phase, may send this gunner to your Used Pile and take Superlaser into hand from Reserve Deck; reshuffle.
front.lore: Most gunners in the Imperial Navy once aspired to be TIE pilots, but lacked sufficient skills to fly starfighters. A few were assigned to the Death Star to man the main artillery.

pulledBy: Set Your Course For Alderaan/The Ultimate Power In The Universe
